OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox has been speaking to
OL,8,FAlison Parr who is full-time carer for
OL,9,Fher daughter Ruby.
OL,11,FThe NHS has apologised to a severely
OL,12,Fdisabled teenage girl for threatening
OL,13,Fto fine her for a prescription she was
OL,14,Fentitled to.
OL,16,FRuby Parr, 17, was diagnosed with a
OL,17,Frare chromosome disorder, Idic 15, at
OL,18,Fjust six months old, and needs round
OL,19,Fthe clock care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
