OL,4,Cover tick box error
OL,6,FAlison, who runs a charity and Ruby's
OL,7,FFund Sensory Centre, said:
OL,8,F"Unfortunately an assumption was made
OL,9,Fthat Ruby, and others like her, can
OL,10,Fopen a letter and read it. But because
OL,11,Fshe can't, she was going to be fined."
OL,13,FThe mum, who is from Congleton,
OL,14,FCheshire, had to get help from Ruby's
OL,15,Fschool, a social worker and her MP to
OL,16,Fget the threat of a fine lifted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
