OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1739349797
OL,3,CDisabled girl threatened with NHS fine
OL,4,Cover tick box error
OL,6,FShe said: 'I'm Ruby's mum and primary
OL,7,Fcarer. I'm OK to look after her 24
OL,8,Fhours a day and could have easily
OL,9,Fresponded to the letter on Ruby's
OL,10,Fbehalf, but that wasn't good enough."
OL,12,FIn a statement, the NHS Business
OL,13,FServices Authority said: "Whilst it
OL,14,Fcustomer service agents followed the
OL,15,Fcorrect procedure to protect patient
OL,16,Fconfidentiality, we are reviewing our
OL,17,Fprocesses."
OL,19,FThe MP of Congleton Sarah Russell MP
OL,20,Fhas raised Ruby's case in Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
