OL,4,Cover tick box error
OL,6,FDescribing the family's situation as
OL,7,F"terrible", she said: "Imagine having
OL,8,Fyour child who's in hospital and
OL,9,Fcoming home to find a letter demanding
OL,10,Fyou pay a fine for a prescription, she
OL,11,Fwas perfectly entitled to. It is such
OL,12,Fa distressing situation."
OL,14,FThe family also sought help from
OL,15,Fdisability advocate Deborah Lawson who
OL,16,Fsaid the situation the family were
OL,17,Fenduring was "blatant discrimination."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
