OL,6,FThe campaigner said: "They were
OL,7,Fdiscriminating against them both -
OL,8,Fthat was wrong. They said they were
OL,9,Ffollowing procedures, but if those
OL,10,Fprocedures exclude the Equality Act,
OL,11,Fthen it needs urgently looking at."
OL,13,FShe added: "I deal with a lot of
OL,14,Fclients who are exacerbated by the
OL,15,Fsystems now, they can't communicate,
OL,16,Fthere is no flexibility in the system,
OL,17,Feven if they ask for reasonable
OL,18,Fadjustments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
