OL,3,CDisabled girl threatened with NHS fine
OL,4,Cover tick box error
OL,6,F"We need to go back to basics and put
OL,7,Fpeople and common sense at the heart
OL,8,Fof these systems."
OL,10,FAlison Parr suggested: "It isn't just
OL,11,Fdisabled people. What if you have
OL,12,Fdementia or you can't read you can't
OL,13,Fmanage that letter? It needs to change
OL,14,Ffor other people."
OL,16,FRuby has now received an apology from
OL,17,Fthe NHSBSA: "If someone claims a free
OL,18,FNHS prescription and we can't confirm
OL,19,Ftheir entitlement, an initial enquiry
OL,20,Fletter is sent to patients.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
