OL,6,F"This gives patients an opportunity to
OL,7,Fcheck their exemption and contact us
OL,8,Fto confirm that they were exempt from
OL,9,Fpaying. If they don't contact us
OL,10,Fwithin 28 days, or if they weren't
OL,11,Fexempt, a penalty charge notice is
OL,12,Fthen issued.
OL,14,F"When we receive evidence that someone
OL,15,Fis exempt from paying prescription
OL,16,Fcharges, their case is then closed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
