OL,6,F"A response to Ms Parr's email of 30
OL,7,FJanuary will be sent to her shortly.
OL,8,FIn this case, whilst our customer
OL,9,Fservice agents followed the correct
OL,10,Fprocedure to protect patient
OL,11,Fconfidentiality, we are reviewing our
OL,12,Fprocesses following Ms Parr's contact
OL,13,Fto us to ensure a better and easier
OL,14,Fexperience should this situation arise
OL,15,Fagain."
